"'''After the Old Life'''" was a [[Music/Legends|song]] by [[Starburst]], released on the album ''[[Only In Your Dreams]]''. It was given a Scarlet rating by the [[Imperial Board of Culture]], meaning it neither protested the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] nor glorified it.

